Package: essora-pymenu
Version: 1.0.1-1
Section: x11
Priority: optional
Architecture: @ARCH@
Installed-Size: @INSTALLED_SIZE@
Maintainer: josejp2424 <puppylinuxjosejp2424@gmail.com>
Depends: libgtk-3-0 | libgtk-3-0t64, libglib2.0-0 | libglib2.0-0t64, libgdk-pixbuf-2.0-0, python3, python3-xdg
Homepage: https://www.essora.org
Description: Native GTK3 application menu for EssoraWM
 A lightweight C/GTK3 menu that loads categories and applications only from
 ~/.config/essorawm/essora-menu.xml. Flatpak, AppImage, Wine and regular
 applications are preserved through the commands generated in that XML.
 The existing Python menu generators and configuration utilities are included.
